    <text>
        <body><div type="bibliography">
                
                <p><bibl><ptr target="#parisipresicce2007b"/>, pp. <citedRange>199-200</citedRange> and fig. 7</bibl>;
                    <bibl><ptr target="#IGCyr"/> <citedRange>118200</citedRange></bibl>.</p>
            </div><div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">
                
                <ab>
                    <lb n="1"/><space quantity="1" unit="character"/> <w lemma="δεκάτα">Δεκάταν</w> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"><certainty match=".." locus="name"/></gap>
	 </ab>
            </div><div type="apparatus" xml:space="preserve">
            
                <p><app loc="1"><lem><space quantity="1" unit="character"/> Δεκάταν <note>from photograph</note></lem>
                    <rdg resp="#parisipresicce2007b"><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> δεκάταν</rdg>
                </app></p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="fr" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>Dîme <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"><certainty match=".." locus="name"/></gap>.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="en" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>Tithe <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"><certainty match=".." locus="name"/></gap>.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="fr" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>Decima <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"><certainty match=".." locus="name"/></gap>.</p>
         </div><div type="commentary">
                
               <p>It is impossible to restore the ancient display only from the quick description of Parisi Presicce. However, the good photograph allows to suspect a 
               large monumental dedication, either made of several blocks or later re-cut. The verb <foreign>ἀνέθηκε/αν</foreign> might remain subaudible, but at least 
               a personal name as subject would have stood in the hidden (or lost?) part. The date proposed here seems a plausible guess.</p>
	<p/>
	<p/>
            </div></body>
